               <p>1694. <persName id="def1-1694-18350817" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def1-1694-18350817" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1694-18350817" type="age" value="53"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1694-18350817" type="surname" value="FEELEY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1694-18350817" type="given" value="THOMAS DOMINICK"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">THOMAS DOMINICK FEELEY</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18350817-1694-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18350817-1694-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18350817-1694-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>, for that he, on the <rs id="t18350817-cd-6" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350817-1694-offence-1 t18350817-cd-6"></join>20th of June</rs>, at <placeName id="t18350817-geo-6">
                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350817-1694-offence-1 t18350817-geo-6"></join>St. Bennet Paul's Wharf</placeName>, feloniously did forge a will and testament, purporting to be the will and testament of <persName id="t18350817-name-125" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-125" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-125" type="surname" value="COLLINS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-125" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350817-1694-offence-1 t18350817-name-125"></join>John Collins</persName>, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18350817-name-126" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-126" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-126" type="surname" value="BEVAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-126" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350817-1694-offence-1 t18350817-name-126"></join>David Bevan</persName> and others.—2nd <hi rend="smallCaps">COUNT</hi>, for felo<lb></lb>niously uttering, disposing of, and putting off a like forged will and testament, well knowing it to be forged, with a like intent.—Two other counts, like the two former, only stating it with intent to defraud <persName id="t18350817-name-127" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-127" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
